OL,3,CMan, 24, dies after being hit by a
OL,4,Cvehicle on M61
OL,6,FA man has died after being hit by a
OL,7,Fvehicle on the M61 motorway.
OL,9,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,10,Fafter the 24-year-old died at the
OL,11,Fscene at 2:55am on Friday 3 April.
OL,13,FThe M61 near Bolton was closed in both
OL,14,Fdirections as officers attended
OL,15,Fbetween junctions three and four.
OL,17,FBoth sides were reopened by 6am.
OL,19,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,20,Fthe driver involved remained at the
OL,21,Fscene, and no arrests have been made.
