OL,3,CMan, 24, dies after being hit by a
OL,4,Cvehicle on M61
OL,6,FA statement from GMP said: "Officers
OL,7,Fare appealing for anyone with any
OL,8,Finformation ` and who may have
OL,9,Fwitnessed the collision ` to please
OL,10,Fget in touch.
OL,12,F"This includes anyone with dashcam
OL,13,Ffootage from around the time."
